stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR

    [*] --> Created : Payment Request Accepted

    Created --> Processing : PaymentInitiated Published

    Processing --> Completed : PaymentCompleted

    Processing --> Failed : PaymentFailed

    Completed --> [*]
    Failed --> [*]

    note right of Created
        Payment record created
        in the same transaction
        as the Outbox entry.
    end note

    note right of Processing
        Waiting for the simulated
        Payment Processor to
        publish the outcome.
    end note

    note right of Completed
        Payment Service lifecycle ends.
        Order Saga begins orchestration.
    end note

    note right of Failed
        No saga orchestration occurs.
    end note